@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangleRoundCorner 10
skinparam rectangleFontSize 14
skinparam rectangleFontStyle bold

title Basic Layered Architecture\nHigher layers depend on lower layers; never the reverse

rectangle "<<Layer N>>\n**Presentation Layer**\nUser interface, views, controllers" as L4 #B3D9FF
rectangle "<<Layer N-1>>\n**Application Layer**\nUse cases, workflows, coordination" as L3 #CCE5CC
rectangle "<<Layer N-2>>\n**Domain Layer**\nBusiness rules, domain entities" as L2 #FFE0B2
rectangle "<<Layer 1>>\n**Foundation / Infrastructure Layer**\nPersistence, utilities, platform abstractions" as L1 #E0CFE8

L4 -[#3366AA]-> L3 : <<allowed-to-use>>
L3 -[#3366AA]-> L2 : <<allowed-to-use>>
L2 -[#3366AA]-> L1 : <<allowed-to-use>>

legend right
  | Color | Layer Role |
  |<#B3D9FF>  | Presentation / UI |
  |<#CCE5CC>  | Application |
  |<#FFE0B2>  | Domain |
  |<#E0CFE8>  | Foundation / Infrastructure |
end legend

note right of L4
  Dependencies flow
  **downward only**.
  Each layer provides
  services to the
  layer above.
end note
@enduml
